{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"color","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute/color","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>« <a href=\"/en-US/SVG/Attribute\" title=\"en/SVG/Attribute\">SVG 属性参考主页</a></p>\n\n<p><code>color</code> 属性用来为 <code><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute/fill\">fill</a></code> 属性、<code><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute/stroke\">stroke</a></code> 属性、<code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute/stop-color\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">stop-color (en-US)</a></code> 属性、<code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute/flood-color\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">flood-color (en-US)</a></code> 属性和 <code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute/lighting-color\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">lighting-color (en-US)</a></code> 属性提供一个潜在的间接值（<code>currentColor</code>）。</p>\n\n<p>作为一个外观属性，它还可以直接用作 CSS 样式表的属性。请阅读 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/color\"><code>css color</code></a> 以了解更多信息。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"用法","title":"用法","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">类别</th>\n   <td>外观属性</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">值</th>\n   <td><a href=\"/en-US/SVG/Content_type#color\" title=\"en/SVG/Content_type#Color\">&lt;color&gt;</a> | inherit</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">规范文档</th>\n   <td><a class=\"external\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/SVG11/color.html#ColorProperty\" rel=\" noopener\">SVG 1.1 (2nd Edition)</a></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"示例","title":"示例","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>svg</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">width</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>100<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">height</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>100<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">xmlns</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>http://www.w3.org/2000/svg<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">version</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>1.1<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>g</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">color</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>green<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>rect</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">width</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>50<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">height</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>50<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">fill</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>currentColor<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">/&gt;</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>circle</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">r</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>25<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">cx</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>70<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">cy</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>70<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">stroke</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>currentColor<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">fill</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>none<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">stroke-width</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>5<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">/&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>g</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>svg</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre></div>\n\n<p><iframe class=\"sample-code-frame\" title=\"示例\" id=\"frame_example\" width=\"100%\" height=\"110\" src=\"https://yari-demos.prod.mdn.mozit.cloud/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute/color/_sample_.example.html\" loading=\"lazy\"></iframe></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"元素","title":"元素","isH3":false,"content":"<p>下列元素可以使用<code>color</code>属性：</p>\n\n<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/SVG/Element#text_content_elements\" title=\"en/SVG/Element#Text_content_elements\">文本内容元素</a>&nbsp;»</li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/SVG/Element#shape_elements\" title=\"en/SVG/Element#Shape_elements\">形状元素</a>&nbsp;»</li>\n <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/stop\"><code>&lt;stop&gt;</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/feFlood\"><code>&lt;feFlood&gt;</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/feDiffuseLighting\"><code>&lt;feDiffuseLighting&gt;</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/feSpecularLighting\"><code>&lt;feSpecularLighting&gt;</code></a></li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性","isH3":false,"query":"svg.attributes.presentation.color","dataURL":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute/color/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"用法","id":"用法"},{"text":"示例","id":"示例"},{"text":"元素","id":"元素"},{"text":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性"}],"summary":"« SVG 属性参考主页","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"color","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"color","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"color","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/web/svg/attribute/color","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/web/svg/attribute/color/index.html","last_commit_url":"htt